videos.description: 1H (16:17) UK Marcus Lee made Dunk. Assisted by Tyler Ulis.
videos.headline: Tyler Ulis throws alley oop to Marcus Lee.

videos.description: Jalen Jones' 3s help Texas A&M get out to an early lead.
videos.headline: Jalen Jones' 3s help Texas A&M get out to an early lead.

videos.description: Super Bowl MVP and Texas A&M alumni Von Miller sitting courtside at the game.
videos.headline: Super Bowl MVP and Texas A&M alumni Von Miller sitting courtside at the game.

videos.description: 1H (9:50) TAMU DJ Hogg made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Admon Gilder.
videos.headline: Texas A&M offensive rebound leads to NBA range 3 from DJ Hogg.

videos.description: 1H (9:27) UK Jamal Murray made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Tyler Ulis.
videos.headline: Jamal Murray responds to Texas A&M's 3 with one of his own.

videos.description: 1H (7:53) TAMU Tyler Davis made Layup. Assisted by Alex Caruso.
videos.headline: Tyler Davis makes the layup while fouled.

videos.description: Jay Bilas compared Isaiah Briscoe's attire to Kyle Macy's after hitting a 3.
videos.headline: "He's dressed like Kyle Macy out there."

videos.description: 1H (0:38) TAMU Alex Caruso made Layup.
videos.headline: A. Caruso made Layup while fouled.

videos.description: John Calipari Haltime Interview
videos.headline: John Calipari Haltime Interview

videos.description: Kentucky's Tyler Ulis throws up the lob behind Marcus Lee, but it's no problem for the Wildcats' big man who grabs it with one hand and throws down the monster dunk.
videos.headline: If you love one-handed alley-oops, this dunk is for you

videos.description: 2H (15:10) TAMU Jalen Jones made Dunk.
videos.headline: Jalen Jones follows the missed layup with a putback dunk.

videos.description: 2H (14:37) UK Jamal Murray missed Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Jamal Murray tries to beat the shot clock but comes up nowhere near the basket.

videos.description: 2H (13:20) TAMU Alex Caruso made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Alex Caruso's 3 causes Kentucky to take a timeout.

videos.description: 2H (12:04) TAMU Alex Caruso Steal.
videos.headline: Great defense from Alex Caruso leads to Texas A&M dunk.

videos.description: Derek Willis goes down with an apparent ankle injury, taken to the locker room.
videos.headline: Derek Willis goes down with an apparent ankle injury, taken to the locker room.

videos.description: 2H (4:59) UK Foul on Isaiah Briscoe.
videos.headline: John Calipari claps sarcastically for Briscoe's offensive foul.
UK vs. TAMU

videos.description: 2H (0:44) UK Marcus Lee made Dunk. Assisted by Tyler Ulis.
videos.headline: Marcus Lee ties it up late with the alley-oop slam.

videos.description: OT (4:31) UK Jamal Murray made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Tyler Ulis.
videos.headline: Jamal Murray getting hot in overtime with a 3-pointer.

videos.description: OT (2:46) TAMU Jalen Jones made Layup. Assisted by Danuel House.
videos.headline: Von Miller pumped about Jalen Jones And-1.

videos.description: OT (1:11) UK Tyler Ulis made Jumper.
videos.headline: Tyler Ulis floats it over Texas A&M.

videos.description: OT (0:23) TAMU Anthony Collins Block.
videos.headline: Collins tracks down Ulis for the block.

videos.description: OT (0:09) UK Technical Foul on Isaac Humphries.
videos.headline: Isaac Humphries commits technical foul after Kentucky key defensive play.

videos.description: In the final seconds of overtime, Texas A&M's Tyler Davis is there to put back the missed shot for the game-winner at the buzzer to beat Kentucky.
videos.headline: Texas A&M wins it at the buzzer in OT on Davis' tip-in
